description: Vyxen is swamped. She has so much work do to and not enough time. Sounds familiar, right? When her man stops by the office, with a bag of new sex toys, Vyxen becomes annoyed and tells him to leave and he does, but only for a moment. You see Richie has a plan, a plan to help alleviate some of Vyxens stress and play one of her favorite games.
title: Beware of Men Bearing Gifts
